service: learn-express-api

frameworkVersion: "4"

provider:
  name: aws
  runtime: nodejs18.x
  stage: ${opt:stage, 'dev'}
  region: ap-southeast-1
  memorySize: 512
  timeout: 30
  environment:
    NODE_ENV: production
    DATABASE_URL: ${env:DATABASE_URL}
    JWT_SECRET: ${env:JWT_SECRET}
    AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID: ${env:AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID}
    AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY: ${env:AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY}
    AWS_REGION: ${env:AWS_REGION}
    S3_BUCKET_NAME: ${env:S3_BUCKET_NAME}
  iam:
    role:
      statements:
        - Effect: Allow
          Action:
            - s3:GetObject
            - s3:PutObject
            - s3:DeleteObject
          Resource: "arn:aws:s3:::${env:S3_BUCKET_NAME}/*"
        - Effect: Allow
          Action:
            - s3:ListBucket
          Resource: "arn:aws:s3:::${env:S3_BUCKET_NAME}"

functions:
  api:
    handler: dist/lambda.handler
    events:
      - httpApi:
          path: "/{proxy+}"
          method: "*"
      - httpApi:
          path: "/"
          method: "*"
    environment:
      NODE_ENV: production

plugins:
  - serverless-offline

custom:
  serverless-offline:
    httpPort: 3500
    host: localhost

package:
  patterns:
    - "!node_modules/**"
    - "!.git/**"
    - "!.vscode/**"
    - "!uploads/**"
    - "!*.md"
    - "!test/**"
    - "!coverage/**"
    - "!src/**"
    - "dist/**"
    - "generated/**"
    - "prisma/**"
